song.title: Fall From Sky
song.info:
Lyrics: 30 feet, 2-1/2 down. Faint shadow 4 forward, 4 forward, drifting to the right a little. Okay 30 seconds Hold Contact light. OK engines stop. Houston, Tranquillity Base here. The Eagle has landed. Roger Tranquillity. We copy you on the ground. You've got a bunch of guys about to turn blue. We're breathing again. Thanks a lot.
The fading day will hide the pain And knowing you will break the chain As time slows down, the hour draws near We conspire to make it clear
You'll never find a better time to make a stand; You'll be fine Know the game and all it holds Just watch it now as it unfolds
